Introduction

Hyeme is a South Korean singer. She is a former member of girl groups BLACKSWAN and RaNia.

On November 17, 2020, Hyeme revealed that she would leave BLACKSWAN after their 'Tonight' promotions, and retire from the entertainment industry following her controversy at the time.
